{
  "chapter": "072",
  "title": "穰侯列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "穰侯出身",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>之母<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>的弟弟。他的祖先是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">羋氏</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "魏冉立昭王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦武王</span>去世，没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>嗣，便立他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲原号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">羋八子（秦宣太后）</span>，待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">羋八子（秦宣太后）</span>改号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>不是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>的生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦惠文后\">惠文后（秦惠文后）</span>，先<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>而死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>有两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟：异<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>的大<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>，名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">厓（魏冉）</span>；同<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羋戎</span>，封为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：羋戎\">华阳君（羋戎）</span>。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>同<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子市\">高陵君（公子市）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子悝\">泾阳君（公子悝）</span>。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>最贤能，从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦惠王\">惠王（秦惠王）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>时就任职当权。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王\">武王（秦武王）</span>去世，诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>争立，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>有能力<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>即位，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">厓（魏冉）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，拱卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>平<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季君</span>之乱，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦武王后\">武王后（秦武王后）</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国去，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>的诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>中不友善的都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了他们，威震<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>年少，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>亲自治国，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>主持政事。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "楼缓免相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>死，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子悝\">泾阳君（公子悝）</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>做人质。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>来相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>不利，于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仇液</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，请求任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>相。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仇液</span>将要起行时，他的客人<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>公对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：仇液\">液（仇液）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>若不听公的意见，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>必会怨恨公。公不如对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>说'请为公不要催<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>急办'。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>请相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>并不着急，反倒可能不听您的。公说了而事办不成，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>必感激公；事办成了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>本来就会感激公。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仇液</span>听从了。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>果然<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">免</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楼缓</span>而任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>相。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "魏冉举白起",
      "text": "想要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕礼\">礼（吕礼）</span>出奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>，派他代替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊阙</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>他们，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>二十四万，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙喜</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">叶</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>托病请辞<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>位，由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">寿烛</span>任相。其<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：寿烛\">烛（寿烛）</span>被免职，再相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">厓（魏冉）</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穰</span>，又增<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>，号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "富于王室",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>被封<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>献出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四百里</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，夺取大小城邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六十馀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>称西帝，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>称东帝。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一个多月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕礼</span>前来，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>各自都去掉帝号复称王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">魏厓（魏冉）</span>再相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>后被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">免</span>。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">免</span>职后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，再相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>后，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白起\">武安君（白起）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>所任用举荐的，两人交情甚好。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>之富，比王室还富。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "须贾说穰侯罢梁围",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，率<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，入北宅，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">梁大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">须贾</span>游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长吏</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王说：'从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏惠王\">惠王（魏惠王）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三梁</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>；<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>不割地，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>仍归还。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>故都，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子良</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>人不割地，故地又回归。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之所以国全兵劲而不被<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>兼并，是因为他们能忍难而慎于割地。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>屡被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>而割地，国家随之灭亡。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>认为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>可效法，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>可为戒。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>是贪暴之国，且无亲情。蚕食<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>，又尽占<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋国</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜暴<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，割走八县，土地还未全部交割，兵又出动了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>哪有满足的时候！如今又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，入北宅，这不是敢<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，而是逼王多割地。王一定不要听他。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>背弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>而与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>讲和，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>怒而离开王，与王争相事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必接受。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>挟<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之兵再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，则国家再想不亡也不可得了。希望王一定不讲和。王若想讲和，少割地要有质押；不然，必被欺骗。'这就是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>听到的，希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>据此考虑。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">周书</span>说'天命不是长久不变的'，意思是幸运不可一再。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜暴<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，割走八县，这不是兵力精良，也非计策精妙，而是天幸居多。如今又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，入北宅，以此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，这是把天幸当作常态。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">智者</span>不会这样。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>尽发其全部百县的胜甲以上的壮丁来戍守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>以为不下<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十万</span>。以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十万之众</span>守<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>七仞之城，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>以为即使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武</span>复生，也不容易攻下。轻率背弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的兵力，去仰攻七仞之城，战<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十万之众</span>，却志在必得，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>以为从<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天地</span>分开以至今日，还不曾有过。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>而不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵必<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">罢</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>邑必失，则前功必弃了。如今<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>正在犹豫，可以少割地收服。希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>乘<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之兵未到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>之前，尽快少割地收服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>正在犹豫得以少割地为利，必然想要，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>就得到所要的了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>气恼<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>抢先自己，必争相事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，合纵由此瓦解，然后<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>可随意选择。况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>得地岂必用兵！割<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋国</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>必献<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">绛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>。又为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>打开两条通路，几乎尽占故<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>之地，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>必献<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">单父</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵可以保全，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>制驭天下，何求不得，何为不成！希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>深思熟虑而不要冒险。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>说：\"好。\" 便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">罢</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "伐魏得三县",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>背<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>合纵相亲。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">暴鸢</span>，得<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三县</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>增加了<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>邑。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "苏代说罢伐齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白起</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡阳</span>又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span>之下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卷</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蔡阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长社</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>。又以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>还给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，并给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>增兵，以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐襄王\">襄王（齐襄王）</span>恐惧，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>暗中送信给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听来往的人说'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将增给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>甲兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万</span>以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>'，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下对敝国之王断言'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王明智而熟于计谋，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>睿智而熟习国事，必定不会增给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>甲兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万</span>以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>'。为什么？三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>相与，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的深仇。百次背叛，百次相欺，不算不信，不算无行。如今<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>反而使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>壮大。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的深仇，不利于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。这是一。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">谋者</span>必定会说'<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>疲敝，然后制约<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之胜'。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>是疲敝之国，以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，就像以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千钧</span>之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>打破溃烂的脓疮一样，必死无疑，怎能使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>疲敝？这是二。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>少出兵，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>就不信任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>；多出兵，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>就受制于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>恐惧，不归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，必归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。这是三。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>割<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>以兵抵御，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>反受敌。这是四。这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>谋<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>谋<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，为何<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>这样聪明而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>这样愚蠢？这是五。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>得<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>而善处之，也必定没有祸患。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>必失<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>。夺取<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的肠胃之地，和出兵恐其不返，哪个有利？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所以说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王明智而熟于计谋，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>睿智而熟习国事，必定不会增给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>甲兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万</span>以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">代</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>不出兵，领兵而归。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "范睢进言免相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>举荐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">客卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灶</span>，想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">刚</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿</span>，以扩大其<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>邑。于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span>自称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张禄先生</span>，讥讽<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">越</span>过三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，以此时机向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>献言说事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>于是任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span>说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦宣太后\">宣太后（秦宣太后）</span>专权，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>间擅权，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子悝\">泾阳君（公子悝）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子市\">高陵君（公子市）</span>之属太奢侈，富于王室。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>醒悟，便<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">免</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>之职，令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子悝\">泾阳（公子悝）</span>等人都出关，去封邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>出关，辎<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千乘</span>之多。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "卒于陶",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>死于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>，就葬于此。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>重新收<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>为郡。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>的亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">舅</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>之所以能东扩疆土，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弱</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，曾称帝于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都西向稽首，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>的功劳。到他贵极富溢之时，一<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫</span>进言游说，便身折势夺而忧死，何况那些羁旅之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>呢！"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏冉\">穰侯（魏冉）</span>有智识，应变多端。 内倚太后，外辅<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>。 四次登上相位，两度封疆列土。 <span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">摧</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">挠</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>。 一<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫</span>进言游说，忧愤而亡。"
    }
  }
}